      <section eId="sec_24_A">
        <num>24-A</num>
        <heading>Closing of banking organizations on Saturday; Sunday, public holiday or Saturday afternoon banking transactions; emergency bank holidays</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_24_A__subsec_i">
          <num>(i)</num>
          <content>
            <p>for the convenience of its\ncustomers or (ii) relating to transactions between that bank and other\nbanks or persons which have remained open for business or are outside\nthe holiday area.\n  j. For purposes of this section, each reference to the superintendent\nof financial services shall be deemed to include any official of the\ndepartment of financial services to whom authority granted by this\nsection has been delegated.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
      </section>
